<p><span>来源：<span>厦门日报</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>
<p>2020-08-28 09:49</p>
<p><i><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200828/5825d596c0824e799ee70a603674a5f6.png" /></i></p>
